BuzzHunter Analytics Division provides marketing intelligence research for fast, effective and cost cautious decisions.

Whether your brand is making its first steps into social media marketing or its well vested into it, you must be able to understand how deeply your customers are connected to your brand.

View more
BuzzHunter specializes in market research based on social media research and analysis:

  • Analysis of relevant influence and opinion leaders
  • Media effectiveness assessment
  • Testing of creative concepts

BuzzHunter is the eyes and the ears of marketing departments.

We provide ongoing feedback and constantly measure the effectiveness of the marketing activity.

View more
Our research provides insight into how different marketing approaches are perceived, to increase the impact of integrated marketing campaigns and also measures the performance of the competition and the eco-system.

BuzzHunter Analytics offers the following services:

  • Dedicated analysts on daily basis
  • Strategic and tactical consulting
  • Multi level weekly reporting
  • Strategic and media planning
  • Influencers reports
  • Trends
  • Messaging analysis

Hanan Gelbendorf

Hanan is a creative business and marketing leader.

In the 15 years prior to starting BuzzHunter, Hanan held leadership roles in high profile corporations such as Eastman Kodak and Creo-Scitex, and within several startups.

Hanan is deeply involved in the Israeli startup scene as the founder of the design- based startup accelerator BABA and as a mentor in high profile startup accelerators such as Microsoft Ventures and MindCET. He teaches UX at the Masters program at Bezalel Academy of Arts and Design.

 

Education:

  • Executive MBA, Penn State
